{
  "texts": [
    "No additional training was done for the real-world deployment.",
    "The TurtleBot2 robot navigated a 21 × 8 m indoor environment with a hallway with obstacles such as door mullions and garbage bins, Fig. 8 The results are shown in Table III.",
    "X-Nav outperformed ViNT and NavDP in both SR and SPL.",
    "These results demonstrate the zero-shot transfer capabilities of X-Nav by successfully adapting to distinct robot embodiments and camera configurations.",
    "We additionally demonstrate X-Nav's ability to avoid local minima (e.g., dead ends), Fig. 9."
  ]
}